core

Class Schedule

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.Schedule

  • public class Schedule
extends java.lang.Object
    The Schedule class represents both a specific date and time as well as a recurrence interval. The date and time are represented by the standard Java Date class. Recurrence is specified via an Enum defined in within the class.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Greg
